<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mein Business</title>
<style>
body{font-family:Arial, sans-serif;margin:0;background:#f5f7fb;color:#222}
header{background:#111;color:white;padding:20px}
nav{display:flex;gap:20px}
nav a{color:white;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold}
.hero{padding:100px 20px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#06b6d4);color:white}
section{padding:60px 20px;max-width:1000px;margin:auto}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px}
.card{background:white;padding:25px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
footer{background:#111;color:white;text-align:center;padding:30px;margin-top:40px}
input,textarea{width:100%;padding:10px;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:15px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid #ccc}
button{background:#4f46e5;color:white;border:none;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer}
button:hover{opacity:0.9}
</style>
</head>
<body><header>
<h2>Mein Business</h2>
<nav>
<a href="#home">Startseite</a>
<a href="#about">Über mich</a>
<a href="#services">Was bieten wir an</a>
<a href="#contact">Kontakt</a>
</nav>
</header><div class="hero" id="home">
<h1>Willkommen bei unserem Business</h1>
<p>Moderne Lösungen für unsere Kunden</p>
</div><section id="about">
<h2>Über mich</h2>
<p>Hier kannst du dein Unternehmen vorstellen. Erzähle etwas über deine Erfahrung, deine Mission und warum Kunden dir vertrauen können.</p>
</section><section id="services">
<h2>Was bieten wir an</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card">
<h3>Service 1</h3>
<p>Beschreibung deiner Dienstleistung.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Service 2</h3>
<p>Beschreibung deiner Dienstleistung.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Service 3</h3>
<p>Beschreibung deiner Dienstleistung.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section><section id="contact">
<h2>Kontakt</h2>
<form>
<input type="text" placeholder="Name" required>
<input type="email" placeholder="E-Mail" required>
<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Nachricht"></textarea>
<button type="submit">Nachricht senden</button>
</form>
</section><footer>
<p>© 2026 Mein Business</p>
</footer></body>
</html>
